Congress, August 2011, pp. 18-20.  
</p>
<p> 89 Schwartz Moshe, The Department of Defense&#8217;s Use of Private Security Contractors in Afghanistan 
<i>and Iraq: Background, Analysis, and Options for Congress,</i> Congressional Research Service, 13 May 
