</p>
<p>Detainees&#8221; in CIA Custody, February 2007, p. 5, available from 
http://www.nybooks.com/media/doc/2010/04/22/icrc-report.pdf. Nine of the fourteen detainees 
reported having been &#8220;brought close to death,&#8221; see p. 18. 
</p>
