Me&#8217;: The Human Rights Crisis in North<i>west Pakistan<b>, </b></i>June 2010, pp. 87-90; Human Rights 
Commission in Pakistan, <i>State of Human Rights in 2010</i>, April 2011, pp. 75-76. 
</p>
