</p>
<p>http://counterterrorism.newamerica.net/drones; also Peter Bergen and Katherine Tiedemann, <i>The Year 
of the Drone </i>(see footnote 124).  
</p>
<p> 128 Amnesty International, &#8216;As if Hell Fell on Me&#8217; (see footnote 124), p. 87. 
 129 Chris Woods, &#8222;Number of CIA drone strikes in Pakistan hit 300,&#8221; 14 October 2011&#8223;, All Stories, 
</p>
<p>Covert Drone War, Human Rights, Bureau of Investigative Journalism. 
